/datum/codex_entry/wire_hacking
	display_name = "Hacking Wires"
	mechanics_text = "With the proper tools, all kinds of machinery can be bent to your will!<br>\
	First use a <l>screwdriver</l> to open the machine's wiring panel.<br>\
	Then, use a <l>multitool</l> and a pair of <l>wirecutters</l> to pulse and cut wires respectively.<br>\
	Some wires can shock you, so watch out! If possible, you should put on <l>insulated gloves</l> while hacking.<br>\
	Your skill in <span codexlink='Electrical Engineering (skill)'>Electrical Engineering</span> will be relevant in this."
